  "text": "Backhaus et al. applied HP to HBSMCs to determine the effect on matrix metalloproteinases (MMPs) and tissue inhibitors of metalloproteinases (TIMP) [CITATION_1] . Exposure of HBSMCs to a sustained HP of 20 cm H 2 O for 7 h ",
